{"schemaVersion":"gas-shunin-manual-law-explanation-audit/v1","reviewedAt":"2026-07-11","qualification":"gas-shunin-otsu","examYear":2020,"sourceQuestionKey":"gas-shunin:otsu:2020:law:q02","questionLabel":"問2","sourceQuestionBodyText":"法令で規定されているガス小売事業者が行う供給条件の説明、熱量等の測定、及び成分の検査に関する次の記述のうち、誤っているものはどれか。","sourceFile":"output/gas-shunin-otsu/questions_json/2020/00_source/question_2020_1.json","explanationPatchFile":"output/gas-shunin-otsu/questions_json/2020/21_explanationText_added/question_2020_1_explanationText_added.json","sourceCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","正しい","正しい","正しい"],"patchedCorrectChoiceText":["間違い","正しい","正しい","正しい","正しい"],"correctChoiceTextMatchesSource":true,"choiceReviews":[{"choiceIndex":0,"verdict":"間違い","directBasis":["ガス事業法第14条第1項"],"basisText":"供給条件は相手方に説明する。"},{"choiceIndex":1,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法第18条"],"basisText":"熱量、圧力及び燃焼性を測定し記録保存する。"},{"choiceIndex":2,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法施行規則第17条第1項"],"basisText":"特定ガス発生設備では燃焼性測定を要しない。"},{"choiceIndex":3,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法第23条"],"basisText":"有害成分量を検査し記録保存する。"},{"choiceIndex":4,"verdict":"正しい","directBasis":["ガス事業法施行規則第22条第1項"],"basisText":"天然ガス主体のガスは所定硫黄等の成分検査を要しない。"}],"changedFields":[],"result":"reviewed_no_explanation_change_needed","sourceUrls":["https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/329AC0000000051","https://laws.e-gov.go.jp/law/345M50000400097"],"lawBasisCorrectedAt":"2026-07-11","lawBasisCorrectionReason":"e-Gov現行条文との再照合により条番号と法令名を補正"}
